     "status" -> "None", "summary" -> 
    "HouseholderMatrix[v] returns the Householder reflection matrix h such \
that v . h is proportional to {1, 0, 0, ...} for vector v. \
HouseholderMatrix[v, k] returns the Householder reflection matrix that \
transforms {vk, ..., vn} with the earlier components {v1, ..., v k - 1} kept \
intact. HouseholderMatrix[m] returns the Householder reflection matrix h such \
that m . h is a lower triangular matrix with all diagonal elements are real \
positive for a rectangular matrix m.", "synonyms" -> {}, "tabletags" -> {}, 
